<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="steal-n">steal <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /stiːl/    美 /stiːl/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>极便宜的东西；易做的事情</strong></h4>
<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="be-a-steal">be a steal</h3>
<p>1.<strong>[非正式用语] 非常便宜：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>By comparison, a fast meal with a hamburger is a steal at $4.80.
通过比较，售价为4.8美元的含汉堡的快餐很便宜。</p><footer>2008 辽宁</footer></div></div>